，没有精神的"},{"type":"entry","text":"downcast [ˈdaʊnkɑːst]","headword":"downcast"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.沮丧的，气馁的"},{"type":"entry","text":"disheartening [dɪsˈhɑːtnɪŋ]","headword":"disheartening"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.使人沮丧的"}]},{"number":769,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"disappoint [ˌdɪsəˈpɔɪnt]","headword":"disappoint"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.（使）失望"},{"type":"note","text":"◎disappoint at对…感到失望"},{"type":"entry","text":"dispirit [dɪˈspɪrɪt]","headword":"dispirit"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使气馁，使沮丧"},{"type":"entry","text":"quit [kwɪt]","headword":"quit"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.放弃"},{"type":"entry","text":"in the gutter 绝望","headword":"in the gutter"},{"type":"entry","text":"feel down 感觉情绪低落","headword":"feel down"},{"type":"entry","text":"get down 使沮丧","headword":"get down"},{"type":"entry","text":"feel blue 心情沮丧","headword":"feel blue"}]},{"number":770,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"low tide 低潮","headword":"low tide"},{"type":"text","text":"let sb. down 使某人失望"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I'm afraid I have to disappoint you. （恐怕我要让你失望了。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：It's nothing. （没事。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：When I get hungry, I get dispirited.（我肚子一饿就感到无精打"},{"type":"text","text":"采。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：What about when you are full? （那你吃饱了的时候呢？）"}]}]}